{
  "stem": "26585.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he said, yes, you will see me soon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He knew he wouldn't come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I just felt it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So when I got home, and my sister was still at the window, I said, don't leave the window.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They have to take him now pretty soon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember what time it was and how long we sat at the window.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, my father walked out of there alone with a suitcase in his hand, and he walked to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I said, where's the Gestapo?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Where's the policeman?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He's walking alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't understand that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We never saw him again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The next day, before mother got back, a Serbian friend came and said, what is your father doing in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I said, our father was arrested by the Gestapo and he was on his way to Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I was on business in [INAUDIBLE] and all of a sudden, I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There's the doctor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I went over to him and said, [NON ENGLISH], [NON ENGLISH], what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And my father said, I'm on my way to Zagreb.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I said, did you see any men?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Nobody.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They were there all the time, but that is how good they were.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Even this business man said, no, he was alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I said, no, he wasn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "They were-- the Gestapo was with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "He said, I saw him get on the train and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They were with him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When mother was in-- got to the general, he was in prison in Zagreb, but we never found out how long.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mother stood in front of the prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't let him in.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
